Class Shuffles

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.Shuffles
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Shuffles
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A container for future shuffles both for Eddystone and iBeacon profiles that is aggregated inside Device object.

    To create new instance of this class, please use Shuffles.Builder.
